The below commands will help you run your python application. Please note that this isn't a web application as we are not hosting this application using any web server.

Login to your ec2-user instance
# switch as root user
sudo su

# Install python
yum install python -y
python --version

# Create app directory
cd /
mkdir app

# Create your python application
cd app/
vi app.py
print("Welcome to my app")

# Run your python application
python app.py
